-- Beijing, Shenzhen Banks Resume Third-Home Lending, Securities Times Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-11T23:51:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-11/beijing-shenzhen-banks-resume-third-home-lending-securities-times-says.html

          
          
             Some banks in Beijing and Shenzhen
have begun lending again for third homes, the Securities Times
reported, citing staff at Industrial and Commercial Bank of
China Ltd. and Bank of Communications Co.  
 Banks in Shanghai, Hangzhou and Nanjing have already
resumed third-home loans, the report said.  
